). This computational simplification led to many insights and became an essential tool for electronic materials, atomic and molecular structure.<\/p>","name":"Walter Kohn","place_of_birth":"Vienna","place_of_death":null,"text":"Walter Kohn ,  born in Austria , Chemistry, 1998","year":1998.0}